How reproducible:
100%

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Deploy undercloud and overcloud
2. Log in to the undercloud UI dashboard
3. Go to deployment roles

Actual results:
Flavor and Images show as Unknown for each deployment role.

Expected results:
Flavor and Images show correct flavor and image for each role. 

